---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Track Your Labs"
  description="Learn how Track Your Labs protects your privacy and handles your personal information."
>
  <main class="flex-1 px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-10 pb-6 md:pb-8 lg:pb-10 pt-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full">
    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-full break-words">
      <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <p class="text-sm mb-2"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> August 12, 2025</p>
      <p class="text-sm mb-2"><strong>Company:</strong> Snowflake Health, LLC ("Snowflake Health," "we," "us," or "our")</p>
      <p class="text-sm mb-6"><strong>Service:</strong> Track Your Labs – <a href="https://www.trackyourlabs.com/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">https://www.trackyourlabs.com/</a></p>
      
      <hr class="my-8" />
      
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-2">TL;DR — Quick Summary</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 break-words">
        <li><strong>Anonymous tool = no data collected or stored.</strong></li>
        <li><strong>HIPAA-compliant processing</strong> ensures security during uploads.</li>
        <li>Waitlist is optional and only used for notifying about upcoming features.</li>
        <li>Your anonymous usage leaves no trails—privacy by design.</li>
        <li>If you provided contact info for the waitlist, you can delete it anytime.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <hr class="my-8" />
      
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. What Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 break-words">
        <li><strong>None, when using the main home page tool.</strong> You can upload up to 50 lab result files—PDF or images—completely anonymously. No personally identifiable information (PII) is collected. Your data disappears when you close the page.</li>
        <li><strong>Optional waitlist participation.</strong> If you choose to join the waitlist, you may provide information such as your name and email so we can notify you once account-based features launch. This information is used <strong>only</strong> for waitlist communication and not tied to any lab results.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <hr class="my-8" />
      
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. What We Don't Do</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 break-words">
        <li>We <strong>do not collect</strong> your personal or health information during anonymous uploads.</li>
        <li>We <strong>do not sell</strong> any data—because we <strong>don't keep any</strong>.</li>
        <li>Anonymous uploads are not stored, so nothing persists beyond your immediate session.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <hr class="my-8" />
      
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. How Your Data Is Handled</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 break-words">
        <li><strong>Infrastructure:</strong> Powered by HIPAA-compliant systems, ensuring secure handling during processing.</li>
        <li><strong>Zero Data Retention:</strong> Once you finish using the anonymous lab tool (e.g., close the page), <strong>no data is saved</strong>.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <hr class="my-8" />
      
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Your Rights</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 break-words">
        <li><strong>Anonymous tool usage:</strong> Your privacy is automatic—there's no data stored and nothing to delete.</li>
        <li><strong>Waitlist entries:</strong> You may request deletion of your provided contact information at any point. Just contact us at <strong>privacy@trackyourlabs.com</strong>.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <hr class="my-8" />
      
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. How Long We Keep Your Data</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 break-words">
        <li><strong>Anonymous processing:</strong> No data is retained—ever.</li>
        <li><strong>Waitlist data:</strong> Retained only as needed to contact you when features launch.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <hr class="my-8" />
      
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="break-words">
        If Snowflake Health makes material changes to this policy, we will notify you—via email if you're on the waitlist—or via an in-app notice or text on the site, <strong>at least 30 days before</strong> any changes take effect.
      </p>
      
      <hr class="my-8" />
      
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="break-words"><strong>Snowflake Health, LLC</strong></p>
      <p class="break-words">Privacy Inquiries / Waitlist or Tool Questions: <strong>privacy@trackyourlabs.com</strong></p>
      <p class="break-words">Website: <a href="https://www.trackyourlabs.com/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">https://www.trackyourlabs.com/</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: none;
  }
  
  .prose table {
    width: 100%;
  }
  
  .prose blockquote {
    font-style: normal;
  }
</style>